1 977, '7 8--

1266
02:37:10,890 --> 02:37:12,810
<i>Moby Dick.</i>

1267
02:37:15,650 --> 02:37:17,610
<i>Dreams in a Drawer.</i>

1268
02:37:18,610 --> 02:37:20,210
<i>The Challenge.</i>

1269
02:37:20,970 --> 02:37:22,730
<i>The Searchers.</i>

1270
02:37:26,370 --> 02:37:28,330
<i>Magnificent Obsession.</i>

1271
02:37:30,770 --> 02:37:32,530
<i>The Cry.</i>

1272
02:37:44,290 --> 02:37:46,090
""Salvatore...

1273
02:37:47,410 --> 02:37:49,090
forgive me.

1274
02:37:50,650 --> 02:37:52,930
When I see you,
I'll explain what happened.

1275
02:37:53,890 --> 02:37:57,170
It was terrible
not to find you here.

1276
02:37:57,210 --> 02:38:02,970
I'm afraid I'll be leaving tonight
for Tuscany with my mother.

1277
02:38:04,130 --> 02:38:05,690
We're moving there.

1278
02:38:06,970 --> 02:38:10,690
But I love only you.

1279
02:38:10,730 --> 02:38:13,890
I'll never be with another man.
I swear it.

1280
02:38:15,890 --> 02:38:20,250
I'm leaving you the address
of a friend where you can write me.

1281
02:38:22,490 --> 02:38:24,450
Don't give up on me.

1282
02:38:27,010 --> 02:38:29,010
Sealed with a kiss...

1283
02:38:30,490 --> 02:38:32,610
Your Elena.''

1284
02:38:36,090 --> 02:38:38,010
<i>When are you leaving?</i>

1285
02:38:39,650 --> 02:38:41,410
This afternoon.

1286
02:38:42,730 --> 02:38:46,170
Elena, perhaps in the future
we could--

1287
02:38:46,370 --> 02:38:49,170
No, Salvatore, there is no future.

1288
02:38:49,530 --> 02:38:51,450
There is only the past.

1289
02:38:52,930 --> 02:38:55,330
Even last night's encounter
was just a dream.

1290
02:38:55,930 --> 02:38:57,930
A wonderful dream.

1291
02:39:00,090 --> 02:39:02,530
When we were young,
we never did it.

1292
02:39:03,530 --> 02:39:04,650
Do you remember?

1293
02:39:07,650 --> 02:39:11,090
<i>Now that it has happened,
I can't imagine a better ending.</i>

1294
02:39:17,730 --> 02:39:20,010
I'll never agree with you.

1295
02:39:21,130 --> 02:39:22,770
Never.

1296
02:41:01,490 --> 02:41:05,370
It's my square.
The square is mine.

1297
02:41:29,010 --> 02:41:31,770
Check the leader.
Roll when you're ready.

1298
02:41:31,770 --> 02:41:35,610
- I liked your film. It was terrific.
- Thanks.

1299
02:41:36,970 --> 02:41:40,210
The distributor is moving up
the release date.

1300
02:41:40,450 --> 02:41:42,650
The press conference
is this afternoon.

1301
02:41:42,650 --> 02:41:45,250
The actors will be there,
as well as the producer.

1302
02:41:45,250 --> 02:41:47,370
We just got official confirmation
of the award...

1303
02:41:47,410 --> 02:41:49,810
but we've already received
loads of telegrams.

1304
02:41:50,770 --> 02:41:52,610
Aren't you happy?

1305
02:41:53,410 --> 02:41:56,130
Sure, fine.
We can discuss it later.